text: Kaysersberg-Vignoble is a new commune in the Haut-Rhin department of eastern France. It was incorporated on 1 January 2016 by the combination of the former communes of Kaysersberg, Kientzheim and Sigolsheim.Arrêté 14 July 2015 == References == Category:Communes in Haut-Rhin Category:2016 establishments in France
